{"type": "article", "id": 54802, "title": "杨洋代言百事，湖人队 1.54 亿美元签下詹姆斯｜乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-07-02T04:05:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5693, "name": "汉堡"}, {"id": 51492, "name": "Mojito"}, {"id": 1128, "name": "LGBT"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 48802, "name": "抖音"}, {"id": 17023, "name": "搜狗"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}, {"id": 4877, "name": "百事"}, {"id": 66, "name": "Facebook"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180702105948UGtN6n7BeaSlzQ3d.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4255960954218820?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=1086393010&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\">杨洋成为百事品牌代言人</a></strong><strong>，</strong>此前百事还找过邓超、李易峰等代言。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702104119Cmja6SvsNKh8BkJl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.523810\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/N7ZQTFgJaZ6MbOC6MGLlDQ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>肯德基为代言人黄子韬、林允拍广告片</strong></a>，推广今天起上市的红黑 CP 堡、鲜果无酒精鸡尾酒“葡萄柚鲜果莫吉托”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702104127eKOF3dfz0u96YrVZ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.026563\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702104230srcBqoRGIe317txu.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.470312\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1720173771/GnYqruFBB?type=comment#_rnd1530501081593\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英格兰队官方微博给哥伦比亚队投票，引发球迷跟风给对手刷票</strong></a>，目前微博上这个“世界杯球队势力榜”的前几名都已经被淘汰。英格兰队官方微博称：请大家保持理智，不要相信封建迷信。同时该队宣布退出投票活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702111458xzaLHG8UgPhM2eif.jpg\" data-ratio=\"2.165217\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/digital/facebook-hits-walmart-p-g-political-ads-warning/314083/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>沃尔玛呼吁</strong><strong>“</strong><strong>把工作岗位带回美国</strong><strong>”</strong><strong>和宝洁支持</strong><strong> LGBTQ </strong><strong>的广告被</strong><strong> Facebook </strong><strong>下架，理由是没有添加政治广告的标签。</strong></a>Facebook 称这两支广告含有政治相关内容，需要增加“由谁支付广告费用”的标签。这是 Facebook 在 5 月份施行的广告新政。在被 AdAge 披露后，Facebook 恢复了这两支广告，不再要求宝洁、沃尔玛添加新的标签。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702110016REP8i4SdmMVX9UIB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.757009\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702110024PFeZ5MQ9wnpNXyE1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.747664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/mediacom-scores-adidas-global-media-buying-win/1486407\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>WPP </strong><strong>旗下公司</strong><strong> MediaCom </strong><strong>获得阿迪达斯全球媒介业务。</strong></a>MediaCom 将负责阿迪达斯与锐步两个品牌的媒介事务，预计这项媒介业务价值 3 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/nba/2018/07/01/lebron-james-lakers-superstar-decision-leaves-nba-world-shocked/749848002/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>勒布朗</strong><strong>·</strong><strong>詹姆斯转会湖人，签下一份</strong><strong> 4 </strong><strong>年</strong><strong> 1.54 </strong><strong>亿美元的合约。</strong></a>周日晚上，经纪公司 Klutch Sports Group 正式宣布了转会消息。布朗·詹姆斯签约品牌耐克已经在 <a href=\"http://store.nba.com/Los_Angeles_Lakers_Gear/Mens_Los_Angeles_Lakers_LeBron_James_Nike_Gold_Swingman_Jersey_%E2%80%93_Icon_Edition/source/share-a-sale?SSAID=1028396&amp;utm_source=Shareasale&amp;utm_medium=affiliates\" rel=\"nofollow\">NBA 商店</a>放出了新款球衣，等待编号确定就会发货。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702110051m086VzyIMrfHaSTG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.qdaily.com/articles/54807.html\">抖音、搜狗被北京网信办、市工商局约谈并，广告业务已经暂停。</a></strong>6 月 30 日，因抖音在搜狗搜索引擎投放的广告中出现侮辱英烈等内容，包括抖音、搜狗在内的 5 家公司被要求整改广告业务，抖音已经暂停了广告投放。目前抖音据说每天收入在千万级别。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：YouTube@<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=errLRzF4RRg\" rel=\"nofollow\">NBA 2K</a></p>"}